  "text": "Ulcer area was measured using plane glass square. Each cell on the glass square was 1 mm 2 in area and the number of cells was counted and the ulcer area was determined for each colon. Ulcer index was measured by summing the lesion score and the ulcer area for each colon specimen [CITATION_1] .",
